00:02:14.932 --> 00:02:22.500
Since I was young, I loved creating something that people enjoyed, 
and making money from it.

00:02:22.600 --> 00:02:29.500
I learned by watching others.
I would nearly skip class to make things like pudding.

00:02:29.600 --> 00:02:33.650
I wanted to make anything and everything.

00:02:34.000 --> 00:02:39.233
His dream as a young boy lead him to Ichigo Daifuku;

00:02:39.266 --> 00:02:44.699
the dawn of a new wagashi.

